{"serial": "62083", "department_serial": 57, "code": "GP7049", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Theory and Identification of Polarizing Microscope", "ch": "偏光顯微鏡原理與鑑識"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "地科三、四可選修"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Kuo, Li-Wei"], "ch": ["郭力維"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "S", "room": "215-1"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "地球科學學系", "en": "Department of Geophysics"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "全部使用", "en": "All"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 13, "remark": {"ch": "地科三、四可選修", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程內容將介紹光學顯微鏡的原理及各種礦物的光學特性。藉由搭配系統性操作觀察與實務介紹，讓學生能瞭解各種礦物之光學特性，以及培養鑑識礦物之能力。(雙語授課)", "en": "“This course will introduce principles of optical microscope and optical characteristics of minerals. On the basis of systematically practical observation and relevant introduction on different groups of minerals, students are expected to both understand the optics of minerals and develop the skill of the determination of mineral phases.(bilingual teaching)“"}, "outline": {"ch": "“1.課程簡介2. 顯微鏡與其校正的介紹3. 礦物之輪廓凸現4. 礦物之光率體5. 礦物之雙折射現象6. 利用附板(accessory plate)判斷礦物光學性質7. 利用干涉圖判斷單軸與雙軸礦物8. 判斷礦物之光學符號與消光角9. 期中考10. 礦物鑑定-橄欖石 11. 礦物鑑定-輝石12. 礦物鑑定-角閃石13. 礦物鑑定-長石14. 礦物鑑定-雲母15. 礦物鑑定-石英16. 礦物鑑定-方解石17. 礦物鑑定-其他18. 期末考“\n實際內容依課堂公告說明", "en": "“1. An introduction to Theory and Identification of Polarizing Microscope2. An introduction to optical microscopy and its adjustment3. Relief of minerals4. Indicatrix of minerals5. Birefringence of minerals6. Determination of optic sign of minerals with accessory plates7. Determination of uniaxial and biaxial crystals with isogyres8. Measurement of extinction angles and optic sign9. Mid-term 10. Mineral identification-olivine11. Mineral identification-pyroxene12. Mineral identification-amphibole13. Mineral identification-feldspar14. Mineral identification-mica15. Mineral identification-silica16. Mineral identification-calcite17. Mineral identification-others18. Final-term“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "透明礦物薄片鑒定手冊，常麗華、陳曼雲、金魏、李世超、于介江，236頁", "en": "“Introduction to Optical Mineralogy, 2nd edition, by William D. Nesse, Oxford, 1991.Mineral Optics principal and techniques, by Wm. Revell Phillips, W.H. Freeman and Company, 1971.“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "80", "en": "80"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗\n\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab", "", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "“期中考  40％\n期末考  40％\n平時小考 20％“", "en": "“Mid-term 40％\nFinal-term 40％\nQuit    20％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期五下午13:00-14:50", "en": "Friday 13:00-14:50"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "應用地球物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n地質\n\n\n、\n\n\n應用地質", "en": "應用地球物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n地質\n\n\n、\n\n\n應用地質"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "獨立思考", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "創新研究", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "組織領導", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際交流", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Independent thinking", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Innovative research", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments"]}, {"competencies": "Capability in organization and leadership", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Internati